This plugin integrates the camunda BPM platform with the Grails web application framework.
*[camunda BPM|http://camunda.org]* is a flexible framework for workflow and process automation.
It's core is a native *[BPMN 2.0|http://www.omg.org/spec/BPMN/2.0/]* process engine that runs
inside the Java Virtual Machine. It is a perfect match for the Spring Framework - and therefore for
*[Grails|http://grails.org]*, too.

Please check out *[camunda.org|http://camunda.org/]* to get started with camunda BPM. Read on here
to get started with the camunda Grails plugin!

